This paper is about intrusion detection system (IDS) which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR). The paper proposes a feature selection model using data mining techniques which involves machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the impact of feature selection on the performance of the IDS which is related to software engineering (cs.SE).
